{"tid":1003351,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本傑尼斯天團「嵐」休團 「國喪級崩潰」恐爆請假潮？","createTime":"2019-01-31T14:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T22:00:25.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"438f18955ee1960d7efb878a7114fa35aedb2815","tid":1003351,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"傑尼斯天團「ARASHI（嵐）」無預警宣布休團，5人合體到2020年底，2021年起隊長大野智將會停止演藝活動，消息傳出後讓眾多粉絲震驚不已，留言更是灌爆了所有相關網頁，更有人形容根本是「國喪級的崩潰」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-01-28/656/20190128001266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-01-28%2F656%2F20190128001266.jpg&h=8c690f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傑尼斯天團「嵐」休團 ，讓粉絲揚言無法接受。<br />\n<br />\n嵐昨晚緊急在於東京都內舉行記者會，隊長大野智含淚表示歉意，表達約3年前就想過自己的生活，當時早已萌生退意，經過多次和成員開會和討論，決定改成訂下活動休止期限，此外更坦言考慮是否向傑尼斯事務所辭職，但在成員阻止下仍持續思考，消息傳出後在日本造成不小衝擊，當時電視台也播出街訪畫面，許多民眾聽到此消息直呼不可置信，日本相關網站也被留言灌爆，紛紛表示：「明天可以放假撫平心情嗎」、「明天各大公司應該會報請假潮」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AA7vTUi.img?h=416&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;u=t&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=964&amp;y=505\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAA7vTUi.img%3Fh%3D416%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26u%3Dt%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D964%26y%3D505&h=e668811f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嵐去年展開出道20週年巡迴公演，年末才在東京巨蛋宣布今年將續開50場演唱會，在最近的面試球賽中，碧咸的大兒子布魯克林（Brooklyn）（圖左）據說已經和阿仙奴簽署這一個賽季的合約。讓237萬位歌迷都能入場，讓粉絲都摩拳霍霍要在官網申請抽票，如此卻傳出2020年12月31日休止活動，讓粉絲心情大洗三溫暖。"},{"pid":"21647206f9ea8f974500d8ae0c5e95168e5dfa10","tid":1003351,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"今次唔得 一揾就揾到"},{"pid":"765fef67126a86a6045b55d931c44c748c3328a3","tid":1003351,"uid":117147,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"第二段足球做咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f60a56ca312c094e560c83808d48ed19d4393e","tid":1003351,"uid":153497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在最近的面試球賽中，碧咸的大兒子布魯克林（Brooklyn）（圖左）據說已經和阿仙奴簽署這一個賽季的合約。</span>"},{"pid":"886b73b62035ffef7ea387b38847d982a39d1c3b","tid":1003351,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4a34e07a837b019c918f265077573abda7abf4","tid":1003351,"uid":215823,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:34:18.000Z","msg":"幾件7頭<br />\n垃圾品味"},{"pid":"9bed35022efb2b7a818ac7dd0d8e6e80f6037db8","tid":1003351,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:35:22.000Z","msg":"完全唔明點解會有人鍾意大野智<br />\n明明70年代樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d880ce78f040f6ddd211c9d754e7c55cea4b3071","tid":1003351,"uid":215823,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bed35022efb2b7a818ac7dd0d8e6e80f6037db8","tid":1003351,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:35:22.000Z","msg":"完全唔明點解會有人鍾意大野智<br />\n明明70年代樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"幾件垃圾<br />\n日本人係咪食慣屎"},{"pid":"1e892a36f8c2797aff516158dfcad1a7b2d2cb82","tid":1003351,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"VS嵐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be95eae8393cab4e7cd2578da78d8e1ed0dc3322","tid":1003351,"uid":6784